###### Requirement: Generic (Polymorphic) Function [*rem*](https://docs.julialang.org/en/v1/base/math/#Base.rem-Tuple%7BAny,%20Any,%20RoundingMode%7D) 

*Compute the remainder of x after integer division by y, with the quotient rounded according to the rounding mode r. In other words, the quantity* ([JuliDoc](https://docs.julialang.org/en/v1/base/math/#Base.rem-Tuple%7BAny,%20Any,%20RoundingMode%7D))

$rem(x,y) := x - y * round(x / y, r),$

*if  $r == RoundToZero$ (default), then the result is exact, and in the interval $[0,∣y∣)$ if $x$ is positive, or $(−∣y∣,0]$ otherwise. See also RoundToZero.* ([JuliDoc](https://docs.julialang.org/en/v1/base/math/#Base.rem-Tuple%7BAny,%20Any,%20RoundingMode%7D))

