###### 3.3.2 *Fermat Test* Function $fermatTest$
*The Fermat test is performed by choosing at random a number a between 1 and n - 1 inclusive and checking whether the remainder modulo n of the nth power of a is equal to a. (SICP, 1996; 2016, p.68) 
